; Coverage test for xact.cc
; Tests the "earlier postings in same transaction" code path in lot matching.
; When a transaction has multiple sell postings, the second sell must account
; for the lots already consumed by the first sell within the same transaction.
; The second -4 sell here spans two lots because the first -3 leaves only
; 2 remaining in lot 1.

2024/01/01 Buy Lot 1
    Assets:Brokerage    5 AAPL {$150.00} [2024/01/01]
    Assets:Cash

2024/02/01 Buy Lot 2
    Assets:Brokerage    5 AAPL {$160.00} [2024/02/01]
    Assets:Cash

2024/03/01 Sell Two Lines
    Assets:Brokerage    -3 AAPL @ $170.00
    Assets:Brokerage    -4 AAPL @ $170.00
    Assets:Cash

test --lot-matching fifo reg Assets:Brokerage
24-Jan-01 Buy Lot 1             Assets:Brokerage             5 AAPL       5 AAPL
24-Feb-01 Buy Lot 2             Assets:Brokerage             5 AAPL      10 AAPL
24-Mar-01 Sell Two Lines        Assets:Brokerage            -3 AAPL       7 AAPL
                                Assets:Brokerage            -2 AAPL       5 AAPL
                                Assets:Brokerage            -2 AAPL       3 AAPL
end test
